reviewText:
It is amazing how detailed Corinne talks about the country and the lifestyle of the Massais. I have been in Kenya but I was not able to learn so much about that country.
Corinne is to admire what she gave up in her former life for her true love. There is just no way to keep these different cultures together. I am curious how her daughter
will react when she meets her father. Waiting for the next book!
